---
title: Mexican Spiced Black Beans with chipotle aioli and BBQ sauce
description: Protein-packed and fibre-filled black beans are smothered in melted cheese, covered in a rich tangy sauce, sprinkled with scallions and set atop a bed of fluffy rice in this Mexican-inspired recipe that's nourishing and tasty in equal measure.
